// SessionPanel
// Side panel listing a session's diagrams, documents, and designs. Items are
// sorted by lastModified (newest first). Supports item click and open-in-new-tab.

FUNCTION formatRelativeTime(ts) -> string
  Just now, Xm ago, Xh ago, Xd ago, or locale date string.

---

FUNCTION getItemIcon(type) -> JSX
  Returns SVG icons for diagram/design/document types.

---

FUNCTION SessionPanel(session, onItemClick, onItemOpenNewTab) -> JSX   EXPORT
  Combines diagrams + documents + designs into a single items array sorted by
  lastModified descending.
  Renders each item with its icon, name, and relative time.
  Clicking an item calls handleItemClick.
  "Open in new tab" button stops propagation and calls onItemOpenNewTab.

---

FUNCTION handleItemClick(item) -> void
  Calls onItemClick(item).

---

FUNCTION handleOpenNewTab(item, e) -> void
  Stops event propagation. Calls onItemOpenNewTab(item).
